Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01’s interlocking circuits have been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the force eject signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s being blocked from the plug side.\NIt’s not being accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Shinji, if we hadn’t done that,\Nyou would have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t make me more angry\Nby saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 has 185 seconds of power\Nleft in its reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s enough to destroy at least\Nhalf of Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he is right now, he’ll do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, listen to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If Commander Ikari hadn’t made that decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone could have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that doesn’t matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard tried to kill Toji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With my hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.86,Title Cards3,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(960,881)}{\fs70}EPISODE 19\N{\fs95}A MAN’S BATTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you’re there, aren’t you?\NSay something! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase the pressure of the LCL to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no time to waste on a childish tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve still got a direct control circuit…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The right breast has been completely dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll begin cleansing the bodily fluids\Nfrom Unit 03 on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can work, it’s not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t just lie in bed during\Nan emergency like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened to Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that they opened the\Nescape hatch with a laser cutter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and removed him forcibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This time…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It might really be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll bet that idiot won’t recover from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn’t injured, so he ought to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s probably dreaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don’t tell me you don’t dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why’s he lyin’ here next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same hospital as my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn’t that Shinji and Ayanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I couldn’t forgive my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finally able to have a comfortable\Nconversation with my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but he won’t try to understand my feelings at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you try to understand your father’s feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you try to understand him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that’s how you run away\Nfrom unpleasantness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with running away\Nfrom unpleasantness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those two arguin’ about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re making a special exception for you.\NJust for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn’t the Class Rep…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like I’m still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? I thought Shinji was here.\NWas I just dreamin’?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Ikari was discharged yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve slept for three days, Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did? For three whole days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Class Rep, did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here as part of my duties\Nas the class representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn’t anything else to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I didn’t get to eat\Nthe lunch you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I’m sorry. They won’t let me\Nbring you lunch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Class Rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell my sister that there’s\Nnothin’ wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, Shinji Ikari.\NThe Commander wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Disobeying orders, private\Nappropriation of an Eva,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,blatant intimidation…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all criminal offenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I don’t want to pilot an Eva anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to stay here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I’ll go back to my teacher’s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’re running away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappoint me.\NI doubt we’ll ever meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that’s my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Erase the Third Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei will be Unit 01’s designated pilot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with the dummy plug as backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you’re leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s true, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Why are you running away now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I envied you. You’re different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Even Toji became an Eva pilot, while I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This line is monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For security reasons, we have\Nterminated this call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that Asuka is so disgusted with me,\Nshe’s not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she didn’t even ask me\Nto say goodbye to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like her. I’m relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep cutting your ties like this,\Nyou’ll have a tough life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s your philosophy, Miss Misato.\NI can’t live like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As I’m sure you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be quite a few restrictions\Nplaced on your activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was Toji chosen to be the Fourth Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All the fourth-level candidates\Nwere in your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found out myself recently\Nthat it was all set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my classmates…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with Suzuhara was a mistake\Nthat can’t be mended with words alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Shinji, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was projecting all of my dreams,\Nhopes and purpose onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I also know that it’s been a huge burden for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we, everyone at Nerv,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,had no choice except to entrust\Nour future to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to remember that one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s a selfish excuse, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll leave your pass code to HQ\Nand your room as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no point. Get rid of them, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t pilot an Eva again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s speaking aggressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve never heard him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:42.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H223CF0&\pos(780,27)}Government Only Special Express R-13\NDeparting 13:38 to New Atsugi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A special state of emergency has been declared\Nfor the Tōkai region.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,137)\c&H56E2FB&}Evacuation Route
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All residents, please evacuate to your\Ndesignated shelters immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeating…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel, battle stations, Level One.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for ground-to-air intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Target status?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s currently advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Komagatake Defense Line\Nhas been penetrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Armor layers one through eighteen\Nhave been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen layers of special armor at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eva won’t make it there in time\Nfor a ground level intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Position Unit 02 for combat\Ninside the Geo-Front,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,directly in front of Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka will engage the target as soon\Nas it breaches the Geo-Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Unit 00?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been placed in the AT Field\NNeutralization Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the left arm hasn’t been\Nregenerated yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it can’t engage in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sortie Rei in Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare a dummy plug as the backup system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Start entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,LCL electrolyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence A10 nerve connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it’s not going to work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulse flow is reversing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 is rejecting the neural connections!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that can’t be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort activation. Sortie Rei in Unit 00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-activate Unit 01 with the dummy plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Unit 00 isn’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter. I’ll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die, I can be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I decided I’d never pilot it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What’re you doing?\NGet into the shelter, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One more hit, and all the armor layers\Nwill have been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m counting on you, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Shinji isn’t here, I can do this by myself.\NPiece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn. Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m neutralizing its AT Field, aren’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won’t it go down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t lose ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut all the nerve connections now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuation training? What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff’s got nothing to do with us pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct hit on the Eighth District!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon the Sixth Shelter! All survivors,\Nhurry to the Third Shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is severely damaged!\NIt can’t continue combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How’s Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s safe. Alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angel has started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s Unit 01’s status?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy plug upload, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Probe insertion, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Start contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulses have vanished.\NIt’s rejecting the dummy plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no use! Eva Unit 01 won’t activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The dummy, Rei…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It won’t accept them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m leaving you in charge for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two and number four will be blocked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take casualties to the Sixth Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry the uninjured to the Third Shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What’re you doing?\NDo you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn’t Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m never going to pilot an Eva again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And since I decided that…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since my moonlighting came out into\Nthe open, I’m not welcome on the combat roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here I am, watering the plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because it’s a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Between Katsuragi’s breasts is nice too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, I want to be here when I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s said if an Angel makes contact\Nwith Adam, who lies below here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,humanity will be eradicated in the Third Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that can stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one thing with power equal\Nto an Angel’s, the Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even a rifle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she mean to blow herself up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,AT Field, full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Unit 00?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What has she done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, the only thing I can do\Nis stand here and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, you have something that you can do.\NThat only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is forcing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Think for yourself, and make\Nthe decision by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about what you ought to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, so you don’t have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct hit on the third foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The final armor plate has melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The Main Shaft is completely exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t Unit 01 ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s rejecting the dummy plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It failed! No response detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep trying. Repeat the process from step 108.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me pilot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me pilot Unit 01, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the pilot of Evangelion Unit 01!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The target has invaded the Main Shaft!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s descending!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s advancing directly towards Central Dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel evacuate. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel evacuate!\NRepeat, all personnel evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 01?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch number five! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 has reached its activation limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The backup isn’t working either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move! Move! Move! Come on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn’t any point to this\Nif you don’t move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move! Move! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move! Come on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don’t move now, if you don’t do it now,\Neveryone’s going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want any more of that! So…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE MOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva has re-activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, this is unbelievable.\NUnit 01’s synch rate is over 400%!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean she’s really awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s eating the Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 01 is taking the S2 engine into herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bindings!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bindings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right. That’s not armor plating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are restraints that allow us\Nto suppress the Eva’s true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now those bindings are being undone\Nby the Eva’s own might.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can no longer stop the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01’s been awakened and set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seele won’t stay quiet for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this also part of your script,\NCommander Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s begun, hasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it all begins here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.38,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1550,760)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.86,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind has been saved\Nby the Eva’s awakening,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shinji is taken into Unit 01\Nand merges with it physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They try to salvage him, but fail.\NWhat was it that the crying Misato saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: “Form of the Mind,\NForm of the Man”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.92,ED Title Cards,,0,0,0,,FORM OF THE MIND, FORM OF THE MAN
